These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-1::.
Beverage: lemonade, sprite, fanta, juice
Hobby: photography, dancing, skydiving, video-games
1. Beverage:sprite is between Beverage:lemonade and Hobby:dancing##2
2. Beverage:sprite is on the left or right of Hobby:photography##3
3. Beverage:sprite is somewhere between Beverage:juice and Beverage:lemonade##7
4. Hobby:dancing is in an even position##4
5. Beverage:juice is on the right of Hobby:skydiving##1
6. Hobby:dancing is somewhere to the left of Hobby:photography##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |     2     |       3       |      4      |
| Beverage   | fanta | juice       | sprite | lemonade        |
| Hobby      | skydiving  | dancing | video-games        | photography |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-2::.
