2. Pet:goldfish is somewhere to the left of Pet:rat##5
3. Pet:goldfish is somewhere to the right of Sport:lacrosse##5
4. Pet:turtle is on the left of Pet:goldfish##1
5. Sport:lacrosse is between Sport:water-polo and Sport:baseball##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |     2      |       3       |    4    |
| Pet     | ferret | turtle       | goldfish         | rat     |
| Sport   | baseball   | lacrosse | water-polo | basketball |

